{
  "stem": "22004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and we was there on that-- we found a little house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we lived there for a couple months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was Ukrainian side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when-- when the Germans was very close, then they attacked Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they attacked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was close already to Rovno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- so I-- I decided to go to Russia-- walk away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were still there-- the whole family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[DRINKS] My sister-- one sister Chaja, she wants to go with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother didn't let her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kiev.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Kiev.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They arrested-- the police, but they let us out right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] So then we came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was working night shift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So his wife recognized me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said I looked like her husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So she knew right who I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, we had to go back to the square.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- we have to come back later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In a couple hours, she was gonna be back from work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, I see I went to-- [? and you ?] see, we were stuck there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, I saw a table where there was sitting a Jewish-- Jewish officer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to  him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I got some packages in the square.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I want-- I want to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wanted my passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said-- he said, he wanted to help us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, I'll give it to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you have to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you don't come back, you're going to be in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I got a [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put me into fix the shoes for the people-- thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
